This patch modifies SDL2.0.4
List of modifications:
- Blending modifications from https://github.com/zielmicha/SDL2
- Revert of commit 7502:6ff02ff3cf06 (mercurial) because freeciv-android has been developped before this change, and this change made freeciv-android's graphics completely unusable.
  Detail of commit 7502:6ff02ff3cf06:
# HG changeset patch
