Updated blend semantics so blending uses the following formula:
    dstRGB = (srcRGB * srcA) + (dstRGB * (1-srcA))
    dstA = srcA + (dstA * (1-srcA))
This allows proper compositing semantics without requiring premultiplied alpha.
